{"id":14972,"date":"2024-02-24T17:59:16","date_gmt":"2020-09-24T12:29:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=14972"},"modified":"2022-05-26T12:43:41","modified_gmt":"2022-05-26T07:13:41","slug":"breakfast-bar-countertop-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/breakfast-bar-countertop-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Breakfast Bar Countertop Ideas For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>As modern kitchens grow from a space to prepare meals to a popular entertainment spot of the home, a breakfast bar countertop is a hot trend in the world of kitchen interiors!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern kitchens are much more than just a place to cook meals. They have instead become the social spots of modern homes to host friends and family in style with breakfast bar countertops.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Breakfast bar countertops can blend in with almost every kitchen style and surely enhance the style quotient of your kitchen. Breakfast bar countertops can be designed and built in varying dimensions, materials and finishes to suit your taste and budget. Regardless of the size of your kitchen &#8211; be it a compact kitchen in a 1BHK or a studio apartment or a huge open kitchen, a breakfast bar countertop is a perfect addition.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>From grabbing a quick bite to chatting with your master chef as she prepares sumptuous meals or even adding an extra workstation a breakfast bar countertop has several functional features and not to mention some stunning aesthetics!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s a lowdown of some of our favourite breakfast bar countertop design ideas to help you pick the best one for your kitchen!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Foldable Breakfast Bar Countertop With Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have an ultra small kitchen with no space to add an island with a breakfast bar countertop, you might just fall in love with this one! This clever breakfast bar countertop idea is custom designed for a compact kitchen. The foldable countertop drops down from the wall giving access to the hidden storage shelves to store condiments, cereal boxes, or cutlery. White bar stools cum chairs add a comfortable seating option and tie the look of this breakfast bar to perfection.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164807\/foldable-breakfast-bar-countertop-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Foldable breakfast bar countertop with storage\" class=\"wp-image-14983\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164807\/foldable-breakfast-bar-countertop-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164807\/foldable-breakfast-bar-countertop-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164807\/foldable-breakfast-bar-countertop-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164807\/foldable-breakfast-bar-countertop-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern Breakfast Bar Countertop For A Classic Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here is an extremely simple yet chic breakfast bar countertop design to please those who believe luxury lies in simplicity.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>An extension to this G shaped kitchen is this stunning breakfast bar with a granite countertop to match the pastel pink cabinetry. Mauve tufted chairs and the overhead pendant light complete the look of this kitchen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you like the look of this breakfast bar countertop but you prefer a different colour palette, you can customise the chair and colour of the cabinetry as per your style and preference. Also, the countertop material can be changed to marble, quartz, tile to match your taste and budget.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164822\/modern-breakfast-bar-countertop-for-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen design with breakfast bar for kitchen\" class=\"wp-image-14985\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164822\/modern-breakfast-bar-countertop-for-kitchen.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164822\/modern-breakfast-bar-countertop-for-kitchen-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164822\/modern-breakfast-bar-countertop-for-kitchen-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164822\/modern-breakfast-bar-countertop-for-kitchen-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Kitchen cabinet design to glam up your interiors\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/17142806\/kitchen-cabinet-design-to-glam-up-your-interiors.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Island That Doubles As A Breakfast Countertop<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are blessed with a big kitchen, you can incorporate a stylish kitchen island so it can double up as a&nbsp; breakfast bar countertop. Or if you already have an island counter in your kitchen, add a couple of comfortable chairs, fix some pendant lights overhead, and you have a DIY breakfast bar countertop! Here, in this kitchen, the island breakfast countertop complements the overall colour scheme of this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/modular-kitchen-design\/\">kitchen\u2019s interiors<\/a> and the cabinetry. The countertop is designed using stunning material quartz, edison light bulbs in tiny cages dangling overhead as pendant lights and two white bar stools cum chairs for seating.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164814\/kitchen-island-breakfast-bar-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen island breakfast bar ideas with couple of comfortable chairs, fix some pendant lights\" class=\"wp-image-14984\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164814\/kitchen-island-breakfast-bar-ideas.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164814\/kitchen-island-breakfast-bar-ideas-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164814\/kitchen-island-breakfast-bar-ideas-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164814\/kitchen-island-breakfast-bar-ideas-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Two Tier Breakfast Countertop For The Best Of Both Worlds!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who doesn&#8217;t like the idea of having a stylish addition to the kitchen that is functional too? This two tier breakfast bar countertop is perfect if you want to add a functional unit to your kitchen. The top tier is a breakfast countertop and the lower can be used as the workstation or a&nbsp; space to serve and stack dishes. This countertop design further has a vertical storage unit with rolling shutters. The marble countertop is an extension of the cooking station and forms a cohesive look with two bar chairs in a complementing colour.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164829\/two-tier-breakfast-counter-for-kitchen.jpg\" alt=\"Two tier breakfast countertop for kitchen counter breakfast bar\" class=\"wp-image-14986\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164829\/two-tier-breakfast-counter-for-kitchen.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164829\/two-tier-breakfast-counter-for-kitchen-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164829\/two-tier-breakfast-counter-for-kitchen-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164829\/two-tier-breakfast-counter-for-kitchen-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Breakfast Bar Countertop With A Bar Unit<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sunday brunches or weekend evening catchups with friends is what new age couples love to do over weekends and free hours. Then why not bring home the happy hour? This breakfast bar countertop is custom designed with a bar unit to perform double duty! This kitchen features a simple wooden breakfast bar countertop to grab a quick bite with wall niches forming a vertical unit with open shelves to flaunt your expensive wine collection. Overhead spotlights and a pair of white cushioned bar stools cum chairs complete the look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164759\/breakfast-bar-countertop-with-bar-unit.jpg\" alt=\"Breakfast bar countertop with a bar unit for your home\" class=\"wp-image-14982\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164759\/breakfast-bar-countertop-with-bar-unit.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164759\/breakfast-bar-countertop-with-bar-unit-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164759\/breakfast-bar-countertop-with-bar-unit-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/24164759\/breakfast-bar-countertop-with-bar-unit-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Design your modular kitchen that are smart like you\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/27152054\/design-modular-kitchens-that-are-smart-like-you.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>And that&#8217;s all for today! This was a list of some of our favourite breakfast bar countertop design ideas. If you are still confused or like different styles and not sure which one to choose for your kitchen here&#8217;s good news for you! We can customise a breakfast bar countertop that matches your taste and requirements. Reach out to us if you want our expert designers to custom design a stylish breakfast bar for you!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Also Read:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/different-types-of-kitchen-layouts\/\">Different Types of Kitchen Layouts<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-cabinet-design-ideas\/\">10 Modern Kitchen Cabinet Design Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-false-ceiling-design-ideas\/\">Kitchen False Ceiling Design Ideas<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form